INSERT INTO `wp_comments` VALUES (18,691,'Pat Speer','zoesozo@bresnan.net','','174.45.164.244','2011-07-24 20:39:54','2011-07-24 20:39:54','Two years ago God gave a Word of Prophecy to us in Cheyenne WY that He was going to bring revival throughout America.  This fire of revival would begin in Alabama, the first state listed alphabetically, and also in Wyoming, the last state alphabetically listed.  As the fire of His Holiness and Presence burned from these two states outward beyond their borders, revival would be spread from the first and the last states to touch every state of this country with His Holiness and Fire.  \r\nWhat you have shared is an encouragement to all of us in Wyoming to believe that He will bring His Word to pass and that we will experience a true revival of Holiness and Fire not only in our state but also in our nation!',0,'1','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 8.0; Windows NT 5.1; Trident/4.0; GTB7.0; .NET CLR 1.0.3705; .NET CLR 1.1.4322; Media Center PC 4.0)','',0,0),(17,702,'kevin Bike4God.com','kbw721@yahoo.com','http://bike4god.com','97.121.80.99','2011-07-24 00:49:13','2011-07-24 00:49:13','Nice ! God rock there world . Spirit have your way . JESUS COME !!!  Love Him and let the Spirit flow . God\'s moving are you ready . Press in for more with all your heart . &gt;&gt;&gt; Its By HIS Spirit , Yes God &lt;&lt;&lt;',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; rv:2.0.1) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/4.0.1','',0,0),(5,303,'Shawn Honnld','shawnsfurniture@gmail.com','','209.193.105.53','2011-07-14 21:39:28','2011-07-14 21:39:28','It has been a privilege to travel with Mark and Cathy and recommend that if you can get to one of their meetings to get there and have the spirit of revival imparted to you. Right on Mark and Cathy!!! Thank you Jesus',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64) AppleWebKit/534.30 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/12.0.742.112 Safari/534.30','',0,0),(6,303,'Charles Hoover','choover3@gmail.com','','216.163.96.235','2011-07-15 03:53:34','2011-07-15 03:53:34','We have had the privilege of praying over venues through out Wyoming and Montana that Mark and Cathy will speaking in the next weeks. It was a blessing and a pleasure beyond anything I have ever experienced. It is an even greater pleasure to call them friend. With all of us together, satan does not have a chance (well we know that already, it\'s in the Bible)',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 6.0; en-US; rv:1.9.2.18) Gecko/20110614 Firefox/3.6.18 ( .NET CLR 3.5.30729; .NET4.0C)','',0,0),(7,77,'Jesse Kade','jessekade@gmail.com','http://www.sharpmachinemedia.com','88.105.202.190','2010-05-22 20:38:11','2010-05-22 19:38:11','Wow, this article is as amazing as the website.  Good work...',0,'1','','',0,1),(8,77,'Heather Alcock','heather@mobilisenow.com','http://www.mobilisenow.com','88.105.202.190','2010-05-23 22:37:10','2010-05-23 21:37:10','I would like to hear this kind of prayer for myself? Do you have any listening resources?',0,'1','','',0,6),(9,540,'Elia','boltinj@yahoo.com','','174.22.226.151','2010-06-18 18:46:20','2010-06-18 17:46:20','Wow, I am really thankful for the way you broke down what it means to come to Him as little children! It\'s always been something I knew and could understand but never really put into words! Thank you for sharing!!',0,'1','','',0,0),(10,540,'Patricia Bento','pmarybento@yahoo.com','','79.169.169.9','2010-11-04 12:19:41','2010-11-04 12:19:41','I always thought it meant to come as innocent trusting little children, but now I understand it in a deeper way. Thanks John.',0,'1','','',0,0),(11,549,'Trevor Lovegrove','trevlin@btinternet.com','','78.100.216.196','2010-06-22 17:14:07','2010-06-22 16:14:07','Well put John, this is just what the Church needs to hear and embrace if we are to be the salt and light that the world needs us to be.\nThe truth of what you have said brings freedom and liberty and far from causing people to sin more as some have suggested, will cause people to want to sin less as the revelation of what Jesus accomplished on the cross  becomes a reality in their hearts.',0,'1','','',0,0),(12,549,'Jesse','jessekade@gmail.com','http://www.sharpmachinemedia.com','208.90.179.132','2010-06-24 05:48:13','2010-06-24 04:48:13','Hey dude, this is good but I\'m getting some questions regarding people who claim to be Christians but they spend Monday through Saturday womanizing, boozing, smoking weed and selling drugs and then spends Sunday at church playing in the worship band.  So what about these peeps.  Can you write an article from that perspective?',0,'1','','',0,0),(14,691,'Susan McKenzie','susan.d.mckenzie@gmail.com','http://teamfamilyonline.com','72.173.64.58','2011-07-17 18:10:57','2011-07-17 18:10:57','A wave of love, sacrificial love... a people who love to serve, always in gratitude and praying without ceasing... that is what I\'ve been seeing... sweeping across the world. People living 1 Corinthians 13... I want to one of such people... revival a a lifestyle. Thanks for an inspiring article, and as a resident of Wyoming, very excited!',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64; rv:5.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/5.0','',0,0),(15,555,'Mark Kuntz','mark@greaterworkshealing.com','','69.146.39.134','2011-07-18 15:17:11','2011-07-18 15:17:11','Praise the Lord!!! This is right on! Until we get a revelation of who we are, we can never do the works that Jesus did. If we see ourselves any less than who Daddy said we were, we will always fall short of our calling and destiny. \r\n  What can you add to the cross ?!!!! What can you add to the finished work of His shed blood who once and for all eradicated and destroyed the handwriting on the wall? The spirit of performance must be squashed in our lives. It was not by works that you were saved and it is not by works that you can receive anything else from Daddy. \r\n  You can stand before both God and satan and declare with all good conscience, \" you have found nothing in me\", I am just as clean and whole and holy as Jesus. Thanks be to God for His mighty blood.',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.0) AppleWebKit/534.30 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/12.0.742.112 Safari/534.30','',0,2),(16,702,'Charles Hoover','choover3@gmail.com','','216.163.96.230','2011-07-20 15:23:22','2011-07-20 15:23:22','Boy that is really great to read. Our spirits are flying high. All praise goes to God.',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 6.0; en-US; rv:1.9.2.18) Gecko/20110614 Firefox/3.6.18 ( .NET CLR 3.5.30729; .NET4.0C)','',0,0),(19,711,'Josh','joshg73@hotmail.com','http://jjomgmoments.blogspot.com','68.111.155.59','2011-07-31 06:16:50','2011-07-31 06:16:50','Good article bro. Fun.',0,'1','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 8.0; Windows NT 6.1; WOW64; Trident/4.0; SLCC2; .NET CLR 2.0.50727; .NET CLR 3.5.30729; .NET CLR 3.0.30729; Media Center PC 6.0; MAAU; .NET4.0C)','',0,0),(28,711,'Susan Darr','susandarr@hotmail.com','','24.19.203.156','2011-08-23 16:17:02','2011-08-23 16:17:02','Enjoyed reading the article.  Found myself wondering about our faith vs the faith of God; is it different or the same? Is it the same element, or maybe it has isotopes like hydrogen (0 neutrons o extra neutron)? Hmmm?  Forgive me, my geek is showing.',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.0; rv:6.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/6.0','',0,0),(23,711,'Mich','michellearchbell@yahoo.com.au','','58.164.213.201','2011-08-18 06:47:02','2011-08-18 06:47:02','Awesome article, thank you for sharing this !',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; MSIE 9.0; Windows NT 6.0; Trident/5.0; yie9)','',0,0),(24,706,'Mich','michellearchbell@yahoo.com.au','','58.164.213.201','2011-08-18 06:50:29','2011-08-18 06:50:29','Praise the Lord , God is moving, thanks for sharing Mark.',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; MSIE 9.0; Windows NT 6.0; Trident/5.0; yie9)','',0,0),(25,702,'Mich','michellearchbell@yahoo.com.au','','58.164.213.201','2011-08-18 06:52:13','2011-08-18 06:52:13','Awesome, thanks for sharing the testimonies, building my faith before I go to Fiji for mission.',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; MSIE 9.0; Windows NT 6.0; Trident/5.0; yie9)','',0,0),(26,303,'Mich','michellearchbell@yahoo.com.au','','58.164.213.201','2011-08-18 06:55:22','2011-08-18 06:55:22','Awesome.. let the Spirit of revival be relaesed across the earth.. revival come to this Great South Land of the Holy Spirit !',0,'1','Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; MSIE 9.0; Windows NT 6.0; Trident/5.0; yie9)','',0,0),(33,691,'Navid','f.snughagealn@nic.ru','http://www.google.com/','151.11.99.228','2011-09-09 18:54:13','2011-09-09 18:54:13','What an awesome way to explain this-now I know evethrying!',0,'trash','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows NT 5.1; SV1)','',14,0),(37,711,'Low Fat Meals','witnessasd@gmail.com','http://www.lowfatdietfoods.net','98.126.95.98','2011-09-16 15:47:17','2011-09-16 15:47:17','Does this site have a page on Facebook?',0,'spam','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows NT 5.1; SV1; .NET CLR 1.1.4322; XMPP Tiscali Communicator v.10.0.2; .NET CLR 2.0.50727)','',0,0);
