INSERT INTO `wp_em_events` VALUES (4,'healing-school',1,1,'Healing School','00:00:00','00:00:00','2011-06-24','2011-06-26',NULL,0,NULL,4,0,NULL,'a:0:{}','2011-06-15 02:23:14',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(5,'healing-school-2',0,1,'Healing School','10:00:00','22:00:00','2011-07-07','2011-07-09','This event starts Thursday night, July 7th at 7:PM, continues Friday night, July 8th at 7P:M and then moves to a different location on Saturday afternoon and evening.\r\n\r\nIt will move to Soldiers of Light at 949 N. Durban on Saturday afternoon July 9th at 1:00 P:M and Saturday evening at 7P:M.\r\n\r\nYesterday a woman with cataracts and much pain was completely healed, could see clearly and had no pain after 5 minutes of personal ministry. Praise God!!! Bring all who have been told they are terminal and who are sick. God will show His love!',0,NULL,5,0,NULL,'a:0:{}','2011-07-08 18:57:34','2011-07-08 18:57:54',0,0,'','0',0,0,0),(6,'is-the-supernatural-real',1,1,'Is The Supernatural Real?','10:00:00','22:00:00','2011-07-14','2011-07-15','This event will be held in George Amos Bldg, the Cottonwood room . We hope to draw in people who are not Christains or church goers who are interested in the supernatural so we can demonstrate the power of our Living God to perform healing and miracles.\r\n\r\nWe will begin Thursday night, July 15th at 7:00 P:M and continue all day Friday from 9:00 A:M till 10:00 P:M with breaks in between.\r\n\r\nHope to see you there. Love Mark and Cathy',0,NULL,6,0,NULL,'a:0:{}','2011-07-08 20:03:05','2011-07-08 20:13:26',0,0,'','0',0,0,0),(7,'revival-meetings',1,1,'Revival Meetings','19:00:00','22:00:00','2011-07-16','2011-07-17','We will be releasing the Spirit of Revival at the Laramie Christain Center beginning Saturday night, July 16th at 7:00 P:M and continuing Sunday morning, July 17th from 10:00 A:M till noon and finishing up Sunday night from 7P:M till 10:00 with a fresh word on doing the greater works. John 14:12\r\n\r\nCome join us for a time of releasing Revival, both personal and corporately as Mark and Cathy preach about how the Spirit of Revival has already been released to each Christain and across the globe.',0,NULL,7,0,NULL,'a:0:{}','2011-07-08 20:21:10','2011-07-14 21:06:45',0,0,'','0',0,0,0),(8,'greater-works-healing-school-and-outreach',NULL,1,'Greater Works Healing School and outreach!','19:00:00','22:00:00','2011-07-21','2011-07-24','We are very pleased to announce an extended Healing School in Sheridan Wyoming. We will begin Thursday night, July 21st at 7:00 P:M and resume Friday morning 10:00 A:M, Friday afternoon at 2:00 P:M, and Friday night at 7:00 P:M, and follow the same schedule for Saturday.\r\n\r\nThe Saturday afternoon schedule will be an outreach into the market place where we lead teams to the streets to love on folks. Come and join us as we see Jesus once again touch peoples lives in a very powerful way, outside of the four walls of the church.',0,NULL,8,0,NULL,'a:0:{}','2011-07-18 15:29:10',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(9,'healing-school-3',1,1,'Healing School','19:00:00','22:00:00','2011-08-11','2011-08-14','This event will begin Thursday night at 7:00 P:M on August 11th and continue with three sessions on Friday, three sessions on Saturday and one session on Sunday Morning at Miracle Place of the Rockies, 6145 N. Montana Ave. Helena Valley, 10:30 A:M. The sessions are morning, 10:00 A:M to Noon, Afternoon, 2 to 5 P:M and Evening, 7 to 10 P:M. The Saturday afternoon session will be a market place outreach into the streets to show how easy it is to love on folks, seeing them touched, blessed, healed, saved and delivered.\r\n\r\nIn our last Healing School, many were healed, as the fire of God fell in Sheridan Wyoming. Many recieved the filling of the Holy Spirit and some were delivered as His glorious presence came and wrecked us for status quo christianity.\r\n\r\nPlease, come and join us.',0,NULL,9,0,NULL,'a:0:{}','2011-07-26 20:39:41','2011-07-27 23:22:37',0,0,'','0',0,0,0),(10,'healing-school-4',NULL,1,'Healing School','19:00:00','22:00:00','2011-08-19','2011-08-20','This Healing School will be only a 4 session school and will include and outreach on Saturday afternoon. We will begin Friday night at 7:00 P:M and resume on Saturday morning at 10:00 A:M, with an outreach at 2:00 P:M and ending in the evening from 7:00 P:M to 10:00 P:M.\r\n\r\nCome and join us and see the goodness of our God!!',0,NULL,10,0,NULL,'a:0:{}','2011-07-26 20:46:46',NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
