rit of Revival has been released in the earth and that God is looking for someone who actually believes that greater is He that is in you than he that is in the word to rise up and begin to act like it. Every since we left Alabama last December God has had us traveling all over the Northwest releasing Revival where ever we go. Go God!!!!','The Spirit of Revival','','inherit','open','open','','303-revision-2','','','2011-07-14 21:32:45','2011-07-14 21:32:45','',303,'http://greaterworkshealing.com/2011/07/303-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(28,1,'2011-06-05 01:38:14','2011-06-05 01:38:14','We have a vision to offer 24-7 on demand Healing ministry to anyone, at anytime, from anywhere in the world. We have launched an online healing room through The Spokane Healing Rooms and the International Association of Healing Rooms (Cal Pierce). Through this cutting edge ministry we are able to offer anyone healing ministry through the internet, in an instant messaging or video messaging chat room. We have seen miracles, healings and even deliverance take place through the internet. There is truly no time or distance in the realm of Heaven and just like the centurion (Mattthew 8:5-13) or the Canaanite woman (Matthew 15:22-28), people are healed long distance.\r\n\r\nIf you would like to be considered for an online healing warrior position or to be an intercessor for this ministry, please fill out the contact us form near the bottom.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Online Healing Rooms\" href=\"http://healingrooms.com/index.php?src=prayerRequest\">Receive online healing</a> | <a title=\"Giving\" href=\"http://greaterworkshealing.com/giving/\">Support us financially</a>','Online Healing Rooms','','publish','closed','closed','','online-healing-rooms','','','2011-06-10 04:10:33','2011-06-10 04:10:33','',0,'http://greaterworkshealing.com/?page_id=28',0,'page','',0),(29,1,'2011-06-05 01:38:01','2011-06-05 01:38:01','','Online Healing Rooms','','inherit','open','open','','28-revision','','','2011-06-