he four walls of the church, especially in emotional and physical healing. This passion also includes releasing the body of Christ into the end timeHealingHarvest by training and equipping the church to live in a lifestyle of divine health and in ministering healing to the nations. They truly believe  all things are possible and love to lead teams into the market place for prophetic evangelism and healing.\r\n\r\nThey offer Healing Schools where they teach people to walk in divine health and minister healing to the world as a lifestyle, taking teams to the streets to show them how easy it is to love on needy people. In the process many are healed, saved, delivered and touched by the Fathers love. <a title=\"Invite Mark &amp; Cathy\" href=\"http://greaterworkshealing.com/events/invite-mark-cathy/\">Invite them to minister in your church!</a>','Mark & Cathy','','publish','closed','closed','','mark-cathy','','','2011-06-12 21:20:22','2011-06-12 21:20:22','',34,'http://greaterworkshealing.com/?page_id=36',0,'page','',0),(37,1,'2011-06-05 01:40:37','2011-06-05 01:40:37','','Mark & Cathy','','inherit','open','open','','36-revision','','','2011-06-05 01:40:37','2011-06-05 01:40:37','',36,'http://greaterworkshealing.com/2011/06/36-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(38,1,'2011-06-05 01:41:09','2011-06-05 01:41:09','Greater Works was founded by <a title=\"Mark &amp; Cathy\" href=\"http://greaterworkshealing.com/about/mark-cathy/\">Mark and Cathy Kuntz</a>.  We have a vision to usher in the end time healing harvest by teaching people how to walk in divine healing, minister healing to others, do market place ministry and leading teams out on the streets to heal, save and deliver.  We are very passionate about revival, miracles and healings and believe the core of the gospel is revival and restoration of the entire man, spirit, soul and body.\r\n\r\nWe have also helped establish worldwide <a title=\"Connect\" href=\"http://healingrooms.com/index.php?src=prayerRequest\">online healing rooms</a> with the <a title=\"International Association of Healing Rooms\" href=\"http://healingrooms.com/\">International Association of Healing Rooms</a>.  We truly believe that all things are possible to those who believe in God.\r\n\r\nIf you\'d like to support Greater Works by through intercession or with another gift or talent, fill out the contact us form below.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Invite Mark &amp; Cathy\" href=\"http://greaterworkshealing.com/events/invite-mark-cathy/\">Invite Mark &amp; Cathy </a>| <a title=\"Giving\" href=\"http://greaterworkshealing.com/giving/\">Support us financially</a>','Greater Works','','publish','closed','closed','','greater-works','','','2011-06-12 21:17:00','2011-06-12 21:17:00','',34,'http://greaterworkshealing.com/?page_id=38',0,'page','',0),(39,1,'2011-06-05 01:40:59','2011-06-05 01:40:59','','Greater Works','','inherit','open','open','','38-revision','','','2011-06-05 01:40:59','2011-06-05 01:40:59','',38,'http://greaterworkshealing.com/2011/06/38-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(40,1,'2011-06-05 01:41:32','2011-06-05 01:41:32','<ol class=\"sof\">\r\n	<li>We believe Jesus Christ is not only the Son of God, but came to earth as God in the flesh. John 1:1-14</li>\r\n	<li>We believe the only way (relationship with God), to the Father is through Jesus Christ. John 14:6</li>\r\n	<li>We believe the only way to enter heaven (eternal life) is through faith in Jesus Christ. Romans 10:9-11</li>\r\n	<li>We believe that the only way to salvation (freedom from eternal judgment) is by Gods grace, through Jesus Christ. Ephesians 2:8-9</li>\r\n	<li>We believe that without faith (opposite of works) it is impossible to please God. Hebrews 11:6</li>\r\n	<li>We believe that faith without works is dead (useless) and that works without faith is dead (useless). James 2:14-24</li>\r\n	<li>We believe that Jesus emptied Himself (stripped Himself) of His Godhead (deity) and humbled Himself as a man on earth. Philippians 2:6-11</li>\r\n	<li>We believe Jesus did nothing on earth (performing countless miracles and healings) as God, but as a man, anointed of the Holy Spirit. Luke 4:1, 14, John 5:19.</li>\r\n	<li>We believe that we (the Body of Christ), His disciples, are all commissioned to heal the sick, raise the dead, cleanse the lepers (heal diseases) and cast out demons. Mark 16: 15-20, Matthew 10:1,8, Mark 6:7,12-13, John 14:12-14, 15:7, 15:16, 16:23, 17:18 , Ephesians 4:11-16, Acts 5:12-16, 1st John 4:17, 3:2</li>\r\n	<li>We believe that all believers (all those that claim Jesus Christ as their Savior and Lord) will do even greater works (miracles, healings, signs and wonders ) than Jesus did. John 14:12</li>\r\n	<li>We believe that we as believers were sent, just like Jesus was sent to the earth, to destroy all the works of the devil and to enforce satan\'s defeat. John 17:18, 1st John 3:8</li>\r\n	<li>We believe that our power source to enforce satan\'s defeat, is only through the promise of the  Father, the Holy Spirit. Acts 2:33</li>\r\n	<li>We believe if any person does not possess the Holy Spirit, that they do not belong to Jesus Christ, that they are nottrulya child of God. Romans 8:9, 14 (Amplified)</li>\r\n	<li>We believe that relationship with Holy Spirit, and the use of His gifts is what marks the New Testament church (His Children) as His own. John 16:7, John 14:26, 1st Corinthians 12, 2nd Timothy 3:5</li>\r\n	<li>We believe that faith should only be in Gods Word, His logos (the written Word) and His rhema, the living Word, Jesus Christ. Hebrews 4:12, John 1:1-14</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nAccording to John 17:18 just as Jesus was sent to the earth by the Father, we also are sent into the world. Jesus perfectly represented the Father (John 17:6 ) in the world, demonstrating His outrageous grace and love for mankind, through healing the sick, raising the dead, cleansing the lepers and casting out demons. Just as Jesus represented the Father, now we are to perfectly represent the Son, by doing exactly what He did. Jesus was our supreme example of what His Body is to do on this earth, to represent Him. We too are sent to destroy the works of the devil, through intimate relationship with Holy Spirit, by healing the sick, raising the dead, cleansing the lepers and casting out demons. The core truth of the simple message of the gospel is revival, the manifestation of Gods love and power over all the power of the enemy. We are here to enforce satan\'s defeat at every turn.','What We Believe','','publish','closed','closed','','what-we-believe','','','2011-06-19 23:33:10','2011-06-19 23:33:10','',34,'http://greaterworkshealing.com/?page_id=40',0,'page','',0),(41,1,'2011-06-05 01:41:23','2011-06-05 01:41:23','','What We Believe','','inherit','open','open','','40-revision','','','2011-06-05 01:41:23','2011-06-05 01:41:23','',40,'http://greaterworkshealing.com/2011/06/40-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(103,1,'2011-06-07 05:00:52','2011-06-07 05:00:52','CONTENTS','Events','','publish','closed','closed','','events','','','2011-06-14 04:36:18','2011-06-14 04:36:18','',0,'http://greaterworkshealing.com/events/',0,'page','',0),(44,1,'2011-06-05 01:44:13','2011-06-05 01:44:13','minitery','','','publish','open','open','','44','','','2011-06-15 15:51:55','2011-06-15 15:51:55','',34,'http://greaterworkshealing.com/?p=44',15,'nav_menu_item','',0),(45,1,'2011-06-05 01:44:13','2011-06-05 01:44:13','yeah','','','publish','open','open','','45','','','2011-06-15 15:51:55','2011-06-15 15:51:55','',34,'http://greaterworkshealing.com/?p=45',16,'nav_menu_item','',0),(140,1,'2011-06-08 02:22:34','2011-06-08 02:22:34','','Get prayer for healing right now in our online healing rooms','','publish','open','open','','get-prayer-for-healing-right-now-in-our-online-healing-rooms','','','2011-06-08 02:47:41','2011-06-08 02:47:41','',0,'http://greaterworkshealing.com/?p=140',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(50,1,'2011-06-05 01:44:13','2011-06-05 01:44:13','What we believe','','','publish','open','open','','50','','','2